{"tid":1766944,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Trump :《香港人權與民主法案》對中美貿易談判無好處","createTime":"2019-12-03T03:10:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T15:33:10.000Z","uid":134071,"like":136,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"9133e2fcb3e6ef14d69391b47340adfc743d13e9","tid":1766944,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T03:10:40.000Z","msg":"多謝佢簽左法案<br />\n不過, 中美貿易協議對美國有咩好處?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191203/s00001/1575335420703\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191203%2Fs00001%2F1575335420703&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRSHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=36a2562c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191203%2Fs00001%2F1575335420703&h=f1552394\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191203/s00001/1575335420703</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年12月3日星期二<br />\n特朗普承認 簽署《香港人權與民主法案》對中美貿易談判無好處 (09:20)<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普上周將《香港人權與民主法案》簽署成法，引起中方強烈不滿，外交部昨日（3日）公布中方反制措施，自即日起暫停審批美軍艦及軍機赴港休整的申請，並制裁多個美國非政府組織。特朗普周一（2日）承認，簽署該法案對中美貿易談判沒有好處。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普啟程往倫敦參加北約峰會前，在白宮南面草坪會見記者。他被問到中美是否仍會達成協議時表示，「中國一直在談判」，相信北京仍然希望達成協議，會拭目以待結果如何。<br />\n<br />\n白宮高級顧問康韋（Kellyanne Conway）則表示，中美仍可能在年底前達成協議，並說正在撰寫第一階段協議的文本。<br />\n<br />\n國務卿蓬佩奧同日在肯塔基州亦談及香港問題，他表示《中英聯合聲明》下，中方有責任及義務履行一國兩制，美國亦努力確保中方這些承諾不是空談。<br />\n<br />\n而主管亞太事務的助理國務卿斯蒂爾韋爾（David Stilwell）表示，《中英聯合聲明》承諾香港有50年自治權，美方希望看到承諾維持下去，希望北京履行承諾，依據《基本法》維繫香港自治。"},{"pid":"7a93c696c6694d1e1c421a055ee09af6a7773eef","tid":1766944,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T03:11:34.000Z","msg":"fake news?"},{"pid":"4c812e1de6b7394136381be13b21281950f8fd0c","tid":1766944,"uid":134071,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"7a93c696c6694d1e1c421a055ee09af6a7773eef","tid":1766944,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T03:11:34.000Z","msg":"fake news?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T03:14:35.000Z","msg":"唔係fake news<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-china-trade/trump-says-us-bill-on-hong-kong-doesnt-help-china-trade-talks-idUSKBN1Y61PA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-usa-china-trade%2Ftrump-says-us-bill-on-hong-kong-doesnt-help-china-trade-talks-idUSKBN1Y61PA&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRSHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=17cfff75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-usa-china-trade%2Ftrump-says-us-bill-on-hong-kong-doesnt-help-china-trade-talks-idUSKBN1Y61PA&h=057ea06e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-china-trade/trump-says-us-bill-on-hong-kong-doesnt-help-china-trade-talks-idUSKBN1Y61PA</a><br />\n<br />\nDecember 2, 2019 / 11:23 PM / Updated 9 hours ago<br />\nTrump says U.S. bill on Hong Kong doesn't help China trade talks<br />\n<br />\nWASHINGTON (Reuters) - U.S. President Donald Trump on Monday said U.S. legislation backing protesters in Hong Kong did not make trade negotiations with China easier, but added he believes Beijing still wants a deal with the United States. <br />\n<br />\nThe law &ldquo;doesn&rsquo;t make it better, but we&rsquo;ll see what happens,&rdquo; Trump said, talking to reporters. He gave no indication when the deal would be finalized."},{"pid":"eb573b0bf5006c897bec490fa565a2de5250a32d","tid":1766944,"uid":41545,"like":146,"dislike":1,"score":145,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T03:17:09.000Z","msg":"真義咪 係呀我知無好處<br />\n但我都簽黎打9支那 吹呀？"},{"pid":"5eda73c627b5f055676e5f540dd3d2180331a6c8","tid":1766944,"uid":33653,"like":72,"dislike":4,"score":68,"quote":{"pid":"eb573b0bf5006c897bec490fa565a2de5250a32d","tid":1766944,"uid":41545,"like":146,"dislike":1,"score":145,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T03:17:09.000Z","ms